## 📌 Project Overview

CafeSite is a SaaS platform that allows cafe owners to create and manage their own professional cafe websites without requiring technical knowledge.

This repository contains the **React + TypeScript front-end prototype** developed for Milestone 4 of the Web Engineering course.

The application demonstrates:

- User authentication (Login / Register)
- Protected routes
- Cafe profile management
- Menu management (CRUD for categories & items)
- Dynamic public website preview
- Admin panel structure
- Fully interactive and responsive UI

---

## 🛠️ Technologies Used

- **React (Vite)**
- **TypeScript**
- **React Router DOM**
- **LocalStorage (temporary data layer)**
- **CSS (custom styling)**
- **ESLint (React Hooks rules enabled)**

---

